 On the Luclin server I thought I had found what it was I was missing. Purpose. So, I set out to recreate a guild I had started in UO there. Well, one good reason I left UO was because I had burnt out as a GM, all work and no play they say... So another move  this one to Torv. That was around the time Kunark went live.I was always expecting to find the magic answer to my purpose goal, always thought hey lets see if I can find it here.. I always found greedy, self centered, non-roleplaying folk who would rather farm Crushbone belts than help someone out in even the smallest way.<br>
 On Thouluxe I came close, 8 levels close. But with the ultimate prrize that close the best guild I have ever been apart of crumbled around us, founding members gone off to greener pastures which soone enough withered there as well.I knew or thought I knew most of the reasoning behind the fall, and when I heard that the RP server was finally being made I knew this would be my home. <br>
 I have roleplayed more here in 7 days played then all of the 50 plus hours on all other characters I have ever played. There are fine folks I have never intereacted with here because as an elf I simply do not understand them. I am sure there are some royal pains here, but there are not too many of anykind and those who are will have to suffer their own company as they advance, I will not put up with them here.<br>
 There are alot of really good folk here and this is where I can finally put down some roots.The rule set mandates planning, it rewards guilds and team work. It sets realistic linguistic obsticals in your way. It supports a world where most folks would choose to associate with their own kind. The economy is how it should be, and the challenges are greater because you have to EARN almost everything.<br>
 I can hardly stomach logging into an &quot;old&quot; server any  longer. The banded mail I where is home crafted(1st time smith), I love it here and plan on staying. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#A62A2A>- </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie>Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1>Firiona Vie General Chat</a> <font color=#A62A2A> - </font><a href="http://www.firiona-vie.com/">Firiona Vie</a><font color=#A62A2A> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.firiona-vie.com/fvchat.html" target="_blank"><h3>Chat Room</a></h3></center> <br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.5<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  